{"comments":"OpticalSize - variable font optical size axis.\n\nControls automatic adjustments for rendering at different sizes.\nAt small sizes: thicker strokes, open counters, wider spacing.\nAt large sizes: finer details, tighter spacing, higher contrast.\n\n## CSS Mapping\nMaps to `font-optical-sizing` (auto/none) and the 'opsz' variation axis.\n\n## Variable Font Axis\nThe 'opsz' axis in OpenType variable fonts. Value typically matches\nthe font size in points, but can be set independently for creative effect.\n\n## History\nTraditional metal type had different designs cut for each size.\n6pt Garamond looked different from 72pt Garamond. Optical sizing\nbrings this craft back to digital typography.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Int"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[64,38],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/OpticalSize.purs","start":[64,21]},"title":"OpticalSize"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","OpticalSize"],"OpticalSize"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[66,48],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/OpticalSize.purs","start":[66,1]},"title":"eqOpticalSize"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","OpticalSize"],"OpticalSize"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[67,50],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/OpticalSize.purs","start":[67,1]},"title":"ordOpticalSize"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","OpticalSize"],"OpticalSize"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[70,39],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/OpticalSize.purs","start":[69,1]},"title":"showOpticalSize"}],"comments":"OpticalSize represents the optical sizing axis value.\nStored as tenths of a point for precision (e.g., 120 = 12.0pt).\nRange is typically 6pt to 144pt, but variable fonts may differ.\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[64,38],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/OpticalSize.purs","start":[64,1]},"title":"OpticalSize"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create OpticalSize from points (clamped to 6-144pt range)\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Number"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","OpticalSize"],"OpticalSize"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[77,37],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/OpticalSize.purs","start":[77,1]},"title":"opticalSize"},{"children":[],"comments":"Auto optical sizing (matches font size) - represented as 0\nWhen rendered, this uses CSS font-optical-sizing: auto\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","OpticalSize"],"OpticalSize"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[85,20],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/OpticalSize.purs","start":[85,1]},"title":"auto"},{"children":[],"comments":"Caption size (8pt) - maximum legibility at small sizes\n","info":{"declTy